<h2>Why Stocky Is Shutting Down</h2>
<p>Shopify announced the permanent shutdown of Stocky effective August 31, 2026. After that date, the app will be removed from all stores and all existing data will be deleted. Shopify has not provided a native replacement — store owners must migrate to a third-party solution before the deadline.</p>
<p>If you currently use Stocky for purchase orders, inventory forecasting, or stock-level monitoring, you need to migrate before August 31, 2026 or lose all your inventory data.</p>

<div class="callout callout-amber">
  <div class="callout-label">&#9888; Data Loss Warning</div>
  <p>Stocky will delete all historical data on shutdown. Export your purchase orders and inventory history from Stocky before August 31, 2026, regardless of which replacement you choose.</p>
</div>

