<h2>How Stocky Swap Works</h2>
<p>Stocky Swap uses Shopify's built-in webhook system and Make.com's free automation tier to log every order to a live Google Sheets dashboard the instant it's paid. No Shopify app install, no subscription, no developer.</p>

